	(hif-tokenize): Handle `?' and ':' as tokens.
	(hif-expr): Parse conditional expressions.
	(hif-or-expr): Parse `||' expressions.
	(hif-and-expr): Renamed from hif-term.
	(hif-conditional): New function to evaluate a conditional
	expression.

